## âœ¨ Features


| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| ğŸ” **Smart Search** | Global & per-chat message search with filters |
| ğŸ’¬ **Messaging** | Send, edit, reply with formatting support |
| ğŸ‘¥ **Contacts** | Search users, get profiles, manage contacts |
| ğŸ“± **Phone Integration** | Message by phone number, auto-contact management |
| ğŸ”§ **Low-level API** | Direct MTProto access for advanced operations |
| ğŸŒ **MTProto API Endpoint** | HTTP endpoint for raw Telegram API calls with entity resolution and safety guardrails |
| ğŸ” **Multi-User Auth** | Bearer token authentication with session isolation |
| ğŸ—ï¸ **Dual Transport** | HTTP (multi-user) and stdio (single-user) support |
| ğŸ“ **Secure File Sending** | URL downloads with SSRF protection, size limits, and local-path restrictions |
| ğŸ“Š **Session Management** | LRU cache, automatic cleanup, health monitoring |
| âš¡ **Performance** | Async operations, parallel queries, connection pooling |
| ğŸ›¡ï¸ **Reliability** | Auto-reconnect, structured logging, error handling |
| ğŸ¯ **AI Optimization** | Literal parameter constraints guide AI model choices |

